script.name: !plugin.autotrade.delivery.go
script.description: Autotrade - Script that runs on delivery ship

line.comment: * v2: waiting for target ship to arrive if first at meetingpoint (G, 02.03.2012)
* don't update gain for new traders, they don't get the costs subtracted, too
* this is already installed in main delivery script
* Only jump if delivery ship is NOT in sector of target ship
* always use fake jump because in XRM small ships can't use JD
* Don't pay back fuel costs because fuel was used up anyway
* don't update gain for new traders, they don't get the costs subtracted, too
* next line was part of trade overview script integration, could possibly be removed
* but I don't dare without checking file thoroughly, some later statement may well expect $ware.price to be inverted
